# NB: benches/ must NOT be excluded from the Docker build context. firefly-eval
# declares an explicit [[bench]] in its Cargo.toml, so cargo needs the source
# file present to parse the workspace manifest during `docker build` — even
# though the bench itself is never compiled for firefly-server. Excluding it
# broke `cargo build` with "can't find `load` bench" (CAP.1 regression, fixed
# 2026-07-19). Integration tests (crates/*/tests/) stay excluded: they are
# auto-discovered, so their absence does not fail manifest parsing.
